{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_31","type":"agent_message","text":"Plan for `US-017` implementation:\n\n1. Add a new platform service module `remote_trigger_dispatch_service` with:\n1. `RemoteTriggerDispatchPolicy` gate flag.\n2. `RemoteTriggerTransport` abstraction for remote dispatch transport.\n3. `PlatformRemoteTriggerDispatchService` implementing `RemoteTriggerDispatchService`.\n\n2. Enforce behavior in service:\n1. Gate check first (`GateDisabled`).\n2. Auth/org context validation using shared auth context (`Unauthorized` when token/org missing).\n3. Transport failures mapped to `TriggerError::UpstreamRemoteError` with no detail leakage.\n\n3. Add tests first (TDD) in `platform`:\n1. Gate-off path returns `GateDisabled`.\n2. Missing auth and missing org return `Unauthorized`.\n3. Transport failure maps to non-leaky `UpstreamRemoteError`.\n4. Local scheduler can still create/list tasks when remote gate is disabled.\n\n4. Wire module exports and dependencies, then run:\n1. `cargo fmt --check`\n2. `cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings`\n3. `cargo test --workspace`\n4. Commit with your exact message."}}
